<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTPA7">
<l>tīyiṟ polikiṉṟa ceñcuṭa rāḻi tikaḻtiruc cakkarattiṉ</l>
<l>kōyiṟ poṟiyālē yoṟṟuṇṭu niṉṟu kuṭikuṭi yāṭceykiṉṟōm</l>
<l>māyap porupaṭai vāṇaṉai yāyiran tōḷum poḻikuruti</l>
<l>pāyac cuḻaṟṟiya vāḻival lāṉukkup pallāṇṭu kūṟutumē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Having been permanently touched by the mark of the temple of [His] holy discus</l>
<l>[with] the splendour of the discus of the red sun that abounds with fire,</l>
<l rend="indent">generation after generation we are servants.</l>
<l>We proclaim many years for [that] mighty man [with] the discus that was brandished at Bāṇa,</l>
<l rend="indent">[whose] army fought [with] deceit,</l>
<l>so that the blood that poured forth from [his] thousand shoulders gushed.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
